title: NPC_DemonicDealer_Start
---
Traveler: Greetings, wanderer. These roads can be dangerous alone. #line:039436e 
Traveler: Let me help you...

-> Accept help \[suffer 5 damage and add broken bottle to your bag\] #line:02d837c 
    <<deal_damage_to_player 5>>
    <<add_item_to_deck a423a676599704f4795f0048c68fc928>>
    Traveler: You're welcome!
-> Accept something that hurts less! \[get 30 coins\]
    <<add_coin_to_player 30>>
    Traveler: Suit yourself... but beware the enemies ahead. #line:00bbfe6 
===

title: NPC_Seahorses_Start
---
Traveler: psst! Mind lending a hand?
Traveler: My babies are scared in these dungeons.
Traveler: Could you get them out of here?
Traveler: Hand them over to the blacksmith and he know how to help them.

-> Accept \[add 3 seahorses to your bag\]
    <<add_item_to_deck f7dd6265cf88ae14e9b3d16c9b7e4bd8 3>>
    Traveler: I owe you the world!
-> Ignore them and walk past... 
    Traveler: That was cruel!
===
